P(X = \frac{1}{2}) = P(\frac{1}{2} \leq X \leq \frac{1}{2}) = F(\frac{1}{2}) - \lim_{x \to \frac{1}{2}^- }F(x) = 1 - \frac{1}{2} = \frac{1}{2}.
\int_0^{1/2} 1 \,dx + \frac{1}{2} = 1.
